{"tid":844420,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個應該增加高鐵站既地方","createTime":"2018-10-02T00:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T00:51:38.000Z","uid":59844,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e36b6f5e947202565bb8a820476f9716316675","tid":844420,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:56:48.000Z","msg":"計九龍站之後，為左方便蝗國人黎香港鳩嗚，應該係港島區加此一個站，最理想地點就係太古，本身近海果邊仲有大把位，商場人流又唔算多，又夠多離地人係果到住，又可以增加當地商鋪消費。<br />\n順帶一提，你地香港人唔好未富先驕，應該人人放奴工假，去少幾次日本，如果唔係就繼續上唔到車果陣又係到怨個政府。你地話係唔係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a1ae25cfb0aec11401d3574de64ae97cb38a22","tid":844420,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:08:33.000Z","msg":"樓主=死窮撚"},{"pid":"ef4e6da4b52b1d6c5a687b165828b6e7df06efc9","tid":844420,"uid":55851,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"禮頓山，太古城，貝沙灣"},{"pid":"cc91c17fed742ee4bf5cb661537b1ab8e359a986","tid":844420,"uid":79382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"添馬公園"},{"pid":"0a142db4bd11d63c1496e98246721156751b4626","tid":844420,"uid":194281,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"禮賓府"},{"pid":"c09ec632587b8eee5d7d507768382cbd647b0386","tid":844420,"uid":209609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"地府"},{"pid":"6722049f2b5e60be580869df8e62ff824226fe1d","tid":844420,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"東龍島<br />\n蒲台島"},{"pid":"8d6eca3305c785c86ffc82e218d546d8ac628e19","tid":844420,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"彩虹，黃大仙，秀乜坪"},{"pid":"68a1a875f68cf7df989856a26b29b2130275ca7a","tid":8